<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="air-v">air <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /eə(r)/    美 /er/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使通风：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We opened doors and windows to <strong>air out</strong> the house.
我们打开了门窗，让房子通通风。</p><footer>2015 四川</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-voice">2.<strong>公开发表 (看法等)(voice)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>air one’s views</strong> / <strong>complaints</strong> 
述说看法/怨言</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>播放；广播：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The TV play is due to air next week. 
这部电视剧定于下周播出。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>airless  /'eələs/ adj   </p></div>